 \"title\": \"Version 1.3.32 for VSCode Released\",\n    \"description\": \"Latest pre-release of Continue VSCode extension with platform-specific builds for Alpine-x64, Darwin-arm64, Linux-arm64, Linux-x64, and Windows-x64 architectures. Extension size approximately 79MB.\",\n    \"updateType\": \"release\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/continuedev/continue/releases/tag/v1.3.32-vscode\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-02-17\",\n    \"community_feedback\": [\n      {\n        \"quote\": \"Continue is an open-source AI code assistant for VSCode that provides GitHub Copilot-like functionality with support for local models via Ollama\",\n        \"source\": \"Technical documentation\",\n        \"sentiment\": \"positive\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"productName\": \"Aider\",\n    \"title\": \"Version 0.86.0 Released\",\n    \"description\": \"Added support for all GPT-5 models, Grok-4 via xai, Gemini 2.5 Flash Lite Preview, and OpenRouter Kimi K2. Improved /clear and /undo command output, fixed model settings replacement, and upgraded PostHog SDK. Aider wrote 88% of the code in this release.\",\n    \"updateType\": \"release\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider/releases/tag/v0.86.0\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-02-18\",\n    \"community_feedback\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"productName\": \"GitHub Copilot\",\n    \"title\": \"Model Picker for GitHub Mobile\",\n    \"description\": \"GitHub Mobile released a model picker feature for Copilot coding agent, available for Copilot Pro and Pro+ users. Enhanced symbol context finding tools for improved code understanding.\",\n    \"updateType\": \"feature\",\n    \"url\": \"https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/changelog\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-02-12\",\n    \"community_feedback\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"productName\": \"Gemini CLI\",\n    \"title\": \"File Reading Functionality Optimized\",\n    \"description\": \"Major optimization of file reading functionality, improving experience from exception-prone to smooth operation. Integrated fixes into latest version with complete changelog available. Team plans further enhancements including binary file preview and incremental reading support.\",\n    \"updateType\": \"feature\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/google/gemini-cli\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-02-09\",\n    \"community_feedback\": []\n  }\n]",
